Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.50,0:00:02.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Good evening!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.71,0:00:06.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We come to you from the Order of the Crest!\NI'm Priestess Priscilla Farnese!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.76,0:00:09.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We're good, thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.84,0:00:11.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, wait a minute, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.63,0:00:15.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The same last name as the former pope.\NIs that the Farnese Crest?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.26,0:00:16.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}No way, right?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.14,0:00:22.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I wish to support Lord Theo\Nin his divine battle to subdue the Chaos.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.35,0:00:24.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Please leave now.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.98,0:00:27.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Company? Are you letting them in?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.19,0:00:30.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's a priestess from\Nthe Order of the Crest.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.36,0:00:34.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,There's no need to welcome the pawn\Nof an annoying religious sect.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.03,0:00:37.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But they appear to have many followers.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.16,0:00:40.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And I hear they go around\Nhealing wounds and illness.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.29,0:00:46.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Rumor has it that you've been\Ntrying to confiscate Crests.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.84,0:00:48.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A Crest is the manifestation\Nof its Lord's will.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.71,0:00:52.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Not something granted by\Nthis so-called god you created!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.80,0:00:55.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So you're a mage, I see!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.51,0:00:59.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A slave to the villainous demon\Nwho controls the Chaos!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.39,0:01:03.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's far more villainous to manipulate\Nhuman souls with your sketchy teachings!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.81,0:01:05.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- Make yourselves–\N- Oh, let them stay.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.15,0:01:08.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,They take care of my people, too, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.57,0:01:09.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Lord Theo!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.07,0:01:12.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So you're Lord Theo!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.53,0:01:19.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Priscilla,\Na priestess of the Order of the Crest.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.08,0:01:22.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I look forward to getting to know you!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.41,0:01:24.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.22,0:03:07.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That was a huge win for us today!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.68,0:03:10.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'd say we've got the pick of\Nthe free Lords around here,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.85,0:03:12.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,either to defeat or join our side!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.31,0:03:17.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Getting the local aristocrat, Sir Neyman,\Nto submit to us was a real coup.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.11,0:03:21.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Meaning that western Savis is now ours!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.12,0:03:25.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It won't be long before\Nyou're crowned King of Savis, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.04,0:03:30.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Lord Theo's goal\Nis not to expand his territories.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.58,0:03:33.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- Huh?\N- Lord Theo is from Systina.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.92,0:03:39.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,He strives to defeat Systina's Lord,\NViscount Rossini, and to save his people.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.01,0:03:42.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But that island belongs to the Union.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.84,0:03:47.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If we take out Rossini, would that make it\Ndifficult to maintain status in the Union?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.72,0:03:48.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.77,0:03:52.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,For that reason, he'll first have\Nto switch to the Alliance eventually.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.19,0:03:56.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Afterwards, he'll make his return to Systina,\Nand take on Viscount Rossini.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.28,0:04:00.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's the first I've heard of this plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.07,0:04:01.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Please forgive me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.11,0:04:05.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I was planning to propose it to you\Nwhen the possibility became more realistic.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.04,0:04:09.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And now I have a recommendation\Nfor you, Lord Theo.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.29,0:04:11.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.29,0:04:13.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Lord Theo, as you're a Baron now...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.54,0:04:16.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,let's choose a family name for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.71,0:04:17.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Family name?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.05,0:04:19.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.26,0:04:22.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,From here on in, Lord Theo,\NI'd like you to call yourself Cornaro.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.59,0:04:24.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Cornaro?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.47,0:04:26.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Who's this Cornaro?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.26,0:04:29.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's the family name of a hero of Systina.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.93,0:04:35.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,One who unified the island, and brought\Nthe magical borders under control,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.31,0:04:39.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,only to be betrayed by the Rossinis,\Nand struck down before completing his work.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.65,0:04:40.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I see!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.94,0:04:44.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's clear why anyone from Systina\Nwould want to take him out.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.16,0:04:47.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So he's gonna proclaim himself\Na descendant of that hero?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.08,0:04:52.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Which will raise the people's hopes\Nfor their hero's return, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.63,0:04:58.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You weren't kidding when you said\Nyou'd stop at nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.88,0:05:00.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not being rash.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.51,0:05:03.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I wouldn't want to tarnish your name\Nin any way, Lord Theo.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.22,0:05:07.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But now I know what\Nyou've got in mind, and I like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.64,0:05:11.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Especially the part\Nabout taking on that Rossini guy!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.89,0:05:16.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well then, let's begin laying the groundwork\Nfor your transfer to the Alliance.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.15,0:05:17.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Moreno.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.44,0:05:21.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'd like you to negotiate\Nwith Viscount Naville, the King of Savis.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.78,0:05:22.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Negotiate?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.53,0:05:25.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,To switch sides to the Alliance,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.78,0:05:28.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Lord Theo will need to go\Nbearing the gift of his current territories.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.95,0:05:33.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So I want you to get the King of Savis\Nto recognize Lord Theo's independence.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.29,0:05:38.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Since Viscount Naville\Nis itching to rule over all of Savis,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.21,0:05:41.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,announcing our independence\Nis not going to sit well with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.76,0:05:43.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I have the utmost faith in your abilities!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.01,0:05:51.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So, Viscount Shakes, the King of Clovis,\Nhas agreed to our secret pact?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.18,0:05:55.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So long as Lord Theo stays out of his lands,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.73,0:05:58.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,he'll recognize his\Ncourt rank and independence.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.81,0:05:59.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Thank goodness.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.65,0:06:02.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much, Sir Sartorus.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.82,0:06:06.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't you overstepping a bit, though?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.07,0:06:06.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.61,0:06:11.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Even though you've been\Nviciously defeating the opposition,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.20,0:06:14.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I've heard no mention of Lord Theo's name.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.37,0:06:16.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,On the contrary,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.75,0:06:22.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I've heard rumors that your Lord is just\Ndecoration, while you're the real mastermind.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.96,0:06:23.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No way...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.30,0:06:27.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But I'm only thinking of Lord Theo.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.38,0:06:30.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not doubting your loyalty.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.05,0:06:35.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But don't you think you might\Nbe ignoring Lord Theo's wishes?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.85,0:06:38.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.98,0:06:44.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Who's there?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.44,0:06:46.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's Siluca.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.49,0:06:51.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Is it something urgent?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.87,0:06:54.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No, I wouldn't say that, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.33,0:06:56.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.25,0:07:01.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry to interrupt you two.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.09,0:07:03.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.92,0:07:07.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I've been informed that a Chaos Disaster\Nhas occurred in the castle town.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.55,0:07:10.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- Let's go!\N- R-Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.64,0:07:17.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.06,0:07:20.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The coal suddenly exploded.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.40,0:07:21.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Damn Chaos!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.40,0:07:23.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- Out of the way!\N- Wounded coming through!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.36,0:07:25.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Boss!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.65,0:07:26.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'll tend to him!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.99,0:07:32.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This is going to hurt,\Nbut please bear with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.20,0:07:38.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Follow me!\NWe'll put out that fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.46,0:07:41.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This should help a little...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.88,0:07:44.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This feeling...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.09,0:07:51.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Siluca!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.76,0:07:53.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What is that thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.60,0:07:57.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A Salamander from Aether?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.60,0:07:59.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Is that a Chaos demon?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.89,0:08:01.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. And it's extremely dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.35,0:08:03.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Then I'm taking it out!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.44,0:08:05.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You mustn't, Lord Theo!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.82,0:08:17.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Slashing at a projection\Nfrom Aether with a sword...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.37,0:08:19.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Is he an idiot or what?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.62,0:08:21.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Lord Theo! Please get away!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.83,0:08:24.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Aishela, draw him towards you for now!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.96,0:08:25.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Leave it to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.76,0:08:40.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Lord Theo, Irvin,\Nhelp the townspeople evacuate.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.85,0:08:41.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.27,0:08:43.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,As for the boss...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.31,0:08:45.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Allow me to heal him.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.98,0:08:48.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Do you have the ability to?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.15,0:08:50.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Please leave it to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.36,0:08:55.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A Crest?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.41,0:08:58.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's all right. Please stay with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.08,0:09:02.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm counting on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.67,0:09:05.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'll take out the demon.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.42,0:09:09.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Water flows from up high to low depths.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.55,0:09:13.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yet at times, its course is reversed,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.59,0:09:15.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,and it becomes a towering wall of water...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.14,0:09:16.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Climb!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.76,0:09:19.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Siluca!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.44,0:09:28.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Siluca!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.19,0:09:31.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Engulf!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.17,0:09:52.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.62,0:10:24.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Siluca!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.12,0:10:27.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Thank goodness!\NYou're finally awake!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.12,0:10:29.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,How long have I been asleep?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.13,0:10:31.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's already noon!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.05,0:10:33.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Where's Lord Theo?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.30,0:10:36.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,He's been dealing with\Nthe aftermath of the fire since last night.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.80,0:10:39.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no! I need to be there, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.81,0:10:46.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Lord Theo!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.94,0:10:48.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,See you, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.23,0:10:51.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Are you feeling well now?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.98,0:10:56.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. Thanks to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.49,0:10:59.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Those wounds...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.16,0:11:01.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You need to have them looked at right away!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.54,0:11:10.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Forgive me for leaving the cleanup to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.79,0:11:12.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Also... um...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.55,0:11:16.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you so much for protecting me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.09,0:11:19.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad you didn't get hurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.01,0:11:20.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.85,0:11:26.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Concerning Clovis, I hear everything went\Naccording to your plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.89,0:11:31.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well, Sir Sartorus gave me a talking-to\Nfor ignoring your wishes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.48,0:11:34.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But I'm grateful for what you're doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.19,0:11:41.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If I hadn't met you, it never would've\Noccurred to me to defeat Rossini.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.66,0:11:44.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But you showed me the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.12,0:11:50.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And now, I'm sure\Nit's exactly what I want to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.04,0:11:54.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,One day, I'm going to lead my forces\Nand arrive on Systina.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.92,0:11:56.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Assuming the family name Cornaro.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.42,0:11:59.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.09,0:12:04.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That said, there are still many\Ntrials and tribulations ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.64,0:12:10.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We'll also be negotiating with the Mage Leader\Nof the Kreische family, who head the Alliance.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.90,0:12:13.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Who is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.90,0:12:16.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Mage Leader Aubeste.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.52,0:12:19.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,My mentor, as well as adoptive father.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.65,0:12:20.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Adoptive father?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.53,0:12:25.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Children with magical potential are taken from\Ntheir biological parents at a young age,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.08,0:12:28.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,and raised by a mage\Nserving as their adoptive father.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.66,0:12:29.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.95,0:12:35.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Then sending his daughter to negotiate\Nshouldn't pose a problem, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.29,0:12:36.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I certainly hope not...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.96,0:12:39.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'll leave it to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.34,0:12:42.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You can't just leave it to me, that won't do!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.05,0:12:47.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Because from here on in,\NI'm going to consult you on everything first.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.35,0:12:51.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not sure that I'll be worthy\Nof your consultation, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.98,0:12:53.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'll see to it that you are!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.52,0:12:57.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well, the negotiations were a bust.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.82,0:13:01.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The King of Savis ended up declaring\Nthat he'd settle it on the battlefield.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.90,0:13:04.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You wouldn't believe how furious he was!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.24,0:13:06.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,"All territories in this nation belong to me,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.49,0:13:10.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,and I can't recognize\Nanyone's independence," he said.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.95,0:13:12.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,He said that, did he?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.16,0:13:14.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,In so many words.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.00,0:13:16.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We don't have much time.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.88,0:13:22.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Let's write to the free Lords\Nand ask them to ally with us, right away!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.77,0:13:39.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We won't stand a chance\Nif no one shows, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.27,0:13:42.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If it comes to that,\NI'll charge the enemy lines alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.90,0:13:45.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That way, your lives will be saved.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.91,0:13:48.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Charging solo into enemy lines?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.24,0:13:52.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I can't let my Lord\Nbe the only one having such fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.54,0:13:55.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I, too, am fully prepared.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.08,0:13:59.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,After all, Lord Theo,\Nyou spared my life in our recent battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.67,0:14:01.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sir Neyman...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.30,0:14:03.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sir Lassic...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.30,0:14:06.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.68,0:14:09.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If they read our letters,\Nand realize the king's desires...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.60,0:14:14.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure the free Lords of Savis\Nwill take our side.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.31,0:14:20.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, but recall on the way over here,\Nthe Lords did let us pass,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.36,0:14:22.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,but they didn't offer any troops.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.40,0:14:29.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The fact we were allowed to pass\Nshows they have affinity for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.24,0:14:34.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So now, as long as even one makes a move...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.41,0:14:38.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Please, somebody come.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.97,0:14:47.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.56,0:14:55.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Is that you, Boss?\NWhat are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.18,0:14:59.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It was Lord Theo and you, Lady Siluca,\Nwho saved our town.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.73,0:15:03.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I can't just look away\Nduring your own crisis.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.07,0:15:09.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad you all feel that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.07,0:15:11.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But this battle's going to be very intense.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.45,0:15:15.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Of course, we're ready to lay down our lives!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.04,0:15:21.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But it's my duty as a Lord\Nto protect my people's lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.00,0:15:22.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Not make you lay them down!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.84,0:15:24.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me, my Lord,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.09,0:15:28.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,but I believe it's also your duty as a Lord\Nto fulfill your people's wishes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.76,0:15:31.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Fulfill their wishes...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.97,0:15:39.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Please, raise your flag, Lord Theo,\Nand grant your people its divine blessing.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.98,0:15:43.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So you won't lose\Nwhat you truly wish to protect.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.23,0:15:47.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What I truly wish to protect...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.90,0:15:50.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Homeland. Family.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.16,0:15:55.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Unflinching courage against formidable foes,\Nwhen fighting for those very things.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.24,0:15:58.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Trust that breeds unswerving solidarity.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.75,0:16:01.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Patience to not give up until the bitter end.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.57,0:16:28.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This is the Patriot's Flag!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.40,0:16:33.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be responsible for all your lives!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.24,0:16:35.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Let's fight together!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.96,0:16:52.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So this is Lord Theo's flag, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.43,0:16:57.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Our allies are sure to come.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.26,0:17:00.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Since these people have come,\Nit is certain to create a massive wave.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.06,0:17:03.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I feel the same way.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.34,0:17:29.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'll show you all!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.30,0:17:31.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,All forces, charge!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.97,0:17:38.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Do not fear! Follow me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.43,0:17:43.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Peter's squad, spreading out!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.52,0:17:48.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Allow me to guide you...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.40,0:17:50.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,to the afterlife!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.67,0:18:07.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Flash of Light!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.13,0:18:14.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We'll pulverize their flank!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.01,0:18:16.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Now! Cut into them!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.31,0:18:24.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.81,0:18:28.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Surge forth!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.82,0:18:35.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Stand your ground!\NHead for the main unit!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.20,0:18:43.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,They're so pesky.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.12,0:18:46.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You men head out!\NGet them in one fell swoop!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.12,0:18:48.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir! Count on us!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.09,0:18:55.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Reinforcements?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.38,0:18:59.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The free Lords have allied with Lord Theo!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.68,0:19:00.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.97,0:19:02.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,King of Savis!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.01,0:19:05.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We've heard all about your ulterior motives!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.35,0:19:10.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If you think you can subjugate our Crests,\Nlet's see you try!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.28,0:19:18.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Lord Naville!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.20,0:19:28.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's futile. Please withdraw for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.05,0:19:34.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Elude!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.80,0:19:38.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Lord Theo!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.09,0:19:40.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The backup forces from\Nthe free Lords have arrived!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.64,0:19:44.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Now! All forces, charge!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.43,0:19:46.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Follow me!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.19,0:19:53.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You bastard!\NI swear I'll get you for this humiliation!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.66,0:20:10.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Did we... win?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.54,0:20:13.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, it's a victory.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.67,0:20:19.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Lord Theo, you've defeated the King of Savis.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.72,0:20:26.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So magnificent!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.77,0:20:30.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Lord Theo must join the Order of the Crest,\Nno matter what it takes!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.77,0:20:37.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Now, if only I can see\Neye to eye with Valdrind...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.86,0:20:45.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's been a long time, Siluca Meletes.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.41,0:20:49.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I had a narrow escape in Aram,\Nthanks to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.62,0:20:56.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I am truly sorry that I wasn't able\Nto save both archdukes, Lady Marrine.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.96,0:21:01.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I know you only had an instant,\Nbut surely there was a better method?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.13,0:21:05.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's been a long time, Father.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.01,0:21:10.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I will remind you that I am now\Nthe Mage Leader of Valdrind's Margrave.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.14,0:21:13.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,My apologies, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.15,0:21:19.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I've already explained my purpose here\Nin the letter I sent in advance.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.74,0:21:26.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,My Lord, Viscount Theo Cornaro,\Nhas conquered the entire Savis region.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.28,0:21:30.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Therefore, he wishes to join\Nthe Factory Alliance.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.41,0:21:33.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And pledge allegiance to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.29,0:21:35.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.33,0:21:39.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,My Lord intends to do everything in his power\Nto aid you, Lady Marrine Kreische,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.38,0:21:41.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,in your conquest of the continent.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.92,0:21:44.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I understand what it is you're proposing.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.26,0:21:47.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Please allow me some time to consider it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.76,0:21:51.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Understood, my Lady.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.11,0:22:05.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,BATTLE FLAG
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.12,0:23:40.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,EPISODE 4:\NDECISION
